OL,3,CTrump says he's 'not happy' with Iran
OL,4,Cas more nuclear talks expected
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump has said
OL,7,Fhe's "not happy" with the way Iran is
OL,8,Fnegotiating, and said more nuclear
OL,9,Ftalks would take place on Friday.
OL,11,FTensions between the United States and
OL,12,FIran remain high after their latest
OL,13,Fnuclear talks in Geneva on Thursday
OL,14,Ffailed to reach a breakthrough, and as
OL,15,FAmerican forces gather in the region.
OL,17,FThe US has spent the last month
OL,18,Famassing a fleet of aircraft and
OL,19,Fwarships near Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
