OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772227258
OL,3,CTrump says he's 'not happy' with Iran
OL,4,Cas more nuclear talks expected
OL,6,FSpeaking to reporters as he left the
OL,7,FWhite House on Friday, Trump said:
OL,8,F"I'm not happy with the fact that
OL,9,Fthey're not willing to give us what we
OL,10,Fhave to have. I'm not thrilled with
OL,11,Fthat. We'll see what happens. We're
OL,12,Ftalking later."
OL,14,FHe added that the Middle Eastern
OL,15,Fcountry "cannot have nuclear weapons".
OL,17,FIran insists it has the right to
OL,18,Fenrich uranium for peaceful purposes
OL,19,Fand denies seeking a nuclear weapon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772227258
OL,3,CTrump says he's 'not happy' with Iran
OL,4,Cas more nuclear talks expected
OL,6,FBut the president has threatened
OL,7,Fmilitary action if Iran does not agree
OL,8,Fto a far-reaching deal to constrain
OL,9,Fits nuclear programme.
OL,11,FIran has in turn threatened to attack
OL,12,FIsrael, raising the risk that military
OL,13,Faction could trigger another regional
OL,14,Fwar.
OL,16,FAsked about the risks of the US
OL,17,Fgetting involved in a drawn-out
OL,18,Fconflict in the Middle East if it
OL,19,Flaunches strikes on Iran, Trump said:
OL,20,F"I guess you could say there's always
OL,21,Fa risk.
OL,26,@|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
