OL,3,CTrump says he's 'not happy' with Iran
OL,4,Cas more nuclear talks expected
OL,6,F"You know, when there's war, there's a
OL,7,Frisk of anything, both good and bad."
OL,9,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,10,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,11,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,12,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,14,FEarlier on Friday, the US State
OL,15,FDepartment said that Secretary of
OL,16,FState Marco Rubio would make a quick
OL,17,Ftrip to Israel early next week.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@eO]
