PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772227258
OL,3,CTrump says he's 'not happy' with Iran
OL,4,Cas more nuclear talks expected
OL,6,FThe US Embassy in Israel had earlier
OL,7,Furged staff who want to leave to
OL,8,Fdepart, joining other nations in
OL,9,Fencouraging people to leave the region
OL,10,Fand signalling that US military action
OL,11,Fmight be imminent.
OL,13,FThe announcement of Rubio's visit
OL,14,Fcould indicate a longer timeline for
OL,15,Fany potential strike.
OL,17,FThe Foreign Office announced it had
OL,18,F"temporarily" withdrawn its staff from
OL,19,FIran in response to the threat of US
OL,20,Fstrikes against the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
