OL,3,CTrump says he's 'not happy' with Iran
OL,4,Cas more nuclear talks expected
OL,6,FIt also said it had moved some staff
OL,7,Ffrom Tel Aviv to "another location
OL,8,Fwithin Israel" and advised against all
OL,9,Fbut essential travel to the country.
OL,11,FOn Thursday, Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,12,FStarmer said the UK was focused on
OL,13,F"supporting the political process"
OL,14,Fbetween Washington and Tehran.
